OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fovernight with a mix of cloud and
OL,7,Fclear spells. Under the clearer skies
OL,8,Fit will turn chilly with the odd mist
OL,9,Fand fog patch.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FMist and fog quickly clearing
OL,12,Fto leave a fine and dry day with
OL,13,Fplenty of sunshine. Warm in the
OL,14,Fsunshine and light breezes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
