OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FCloudier to start on Tuesday. Then
OL,7,Flots of sunshine apart from some
OL,8,Fshowers in parts of Cornwall on
OL,9,FThursday. Feeling warm. Winds
OL,10,Fstrengthening by Wednesday making it
OL,11,Ffeel slightly cooler.
